**URL:** github.com/AgentMindCloud/vscode-grok-yaml

### GitHub description
```
Official community VS Code extension for the GrokInstall ecosystem. Full IntelliSense, live validation, safety scanning, template gallery, and one-click deployment for all 14 YAML standards. Built for developers shipping Grok-native agents on X.
```

### Topics
