The official community VS Code extension for the GrokInstall ecosystem. Get full IntelliSense and live validation for all 14 YAML standards, run the safety scanner inline, browse and clone agent templates without leaving the editor, and deploy to X with one command. Free, open-source, and built by @JanSol0s.
