### Initial files Claude Code will create in Session 7
- `package.json` — extension manifest with publisher, displayName, contributes.yamlValidation
- `src/extension.ts` — activation, schema registration
- `src/diagnostics/`, `src/status/`, `src/commands/`, `src/webview/`, `src/snippets/`
- `schemas/` — local copy of all 14 JSON schemas from grok-yaml-standards
- `assets/icon.png` — 128×128 brand icon
- `README.md` — using premium template
- `docs/index.html` — premium hub (with chatbot widget embedded, data-repo-id="vscode-grok-yaml")
- `CHANGELOG.md`, `LICENSE`, `SECURITY.md`, `CONTRIBUTING.md`

### Marketplace listing (when published to VS Code Marketplace, after Session 8)
