### Privacy / abuse / cost notes
- API key NEVER in widget code or any frontend file. It only exists in Render env.
- Every request requires a valid `repo_id` from the `/repos/` config — unknown IDs are 404.
- Rate limit defaults: 20/session/hour, 200/session/day, 50/IP/hour.
- Cost cap: server refuses new requests when monthly spend exceeds GROK_MONTHLY_CAP_USD.
- No PII collected. Session IDs are random UUIDs in the widget's localStorage.
- Feedback (thumbs) stored to local JSONL or Vercel KV for review.

